OL,6,FA call has been made for records
OL,7,Frelating to former mother and baby
OL,8,Finstitutions, Magdalen Laundries and
OL,9,Fworkhouses in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FIt comes as part of a Truth Recovery
OL,12,FProgramme to investigate what happened
OL,13,Fat those institutions which operated
OL,14,Fin the region from 1922 to 1995.
OL,16,FMore than 14,000 women and girls are
OL,17,Fthought to have passed through these
OL,18,Ftype of institutions with many found
OL,19,Fto have been mistreated, held against
OL,20,Ftheir will and forced to give up
OL,21,Fchildren for adoption.
