OL,6,FIn 2021, Stormont was urged to
OL,7,Festablish a public inquiry to
OL,8,Finvestigate the institutions and
OL,9,Fdeliver financial redress to survivors.
OL,11,FA consultation on proposals for a
OL,12,Fpublic inquiry and an associated
OL,13,Fredress scheme has been carried out.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, a team at the Public Record
OL,16,FOffice of Northern Ireland (PRONI) has
OL,17,Fbeen identifying and preserving
OL,18,Frecords relating to the former
OL,19,Finstitutions.
