OL,6,F"As well as records of the
OL,7,Finstitutions, the team at PRONI is
OL,8,Finterested in acquiring other related
OL,9,Fdocuments which may have survived from
OL,10,Fthis period, for example, records of
OL,11,Fprivate maternity nursing homes, the
OL,12,Fpapers of former midwives or social
OL,13,Fworkers, or letters or diaries of
OL,14,Findividuals whose lives were touched
OL,15,Fby these issues," he said.
