OL,6,F"If you discover any historical
OL,7,Fdocuments which you think may be of
OL,8,Finterest to the Truth Recovery
OL,9,FProgramme, please contact the PRONI
OL,10,FTruth Recovery Records team via
OL,11,Faccess@communities-ni.gov.uk."
OL,13,FHe added: "We understand this may be a
OL,14,Fvery difficult and emotive subject,
OL,15,Fparticularly for individuals and
OL,16,Ffamilies personally affected.
OL,18,F"We would like to assure the public
OL,19,Fthat any contact with the team will be
OL,20,Ftreated sensitively and
OL,21,Fconfidentially."
